rows.label: tlk43400541_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Gromrice is the Invidians' staple food.
It's cultivated enthusiastically in the
capital, Fons Maim.

rows.label: tlk43400541_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The interesting thing is, its name
changes depending on how you cook it.

rows.label: tlk43400541_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If you knead it and finely chop it,
that's called Fidel, or you can flatten
it out, then it's a Glarna.

rows.label: tlk43400541_01_msg0005
rows.name:
To think I'm supporting Invidian food
culture gives me such a buzz!
